item.title: Shortcuts
item.description: Shortcuts Table 1: Magit Shortcuts Keys Function Description SPC g s d d Diff between local and remote (type master in prompt) SPC g s b x Delete a branch SPC g b Git blame Git blame Table 2: Other shortcuts Keys Function Description d d On a commit views changes
